msgstr "فیلترها"

#: general/templates/general/about-search.html:44
msgid ""
"There are numerous filters which can be used to help refine searches and "
"navigate the IEDC's extensive corpus. If you were only interested in "
"documents written in New Persian, for example, you can select 'New Persian "
